	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On CHRROM boards, the pin CHR /WR is not connected, so writes to CHR ROM have absolutely no effect (they don't even make a bus conflict like writes to PRG ROM).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


